{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"5 Langkah Bikin Komik Ala Komikus Profesional","content":"<p>Sebetulnya ada banyak aspek dan poin penting untuk bikin komik, kali ini CIAYO Comics berusaha memberikan tips mudah kepada pembaca yang belum pernah bikin komik untuk mencoba membuat komikmu yang pertama!</p>\n<p>1. Temukan sebuah konsep yang menarik.</p>\n<p>Pilihlah tema dan isu yang kamu kenal dengan baik. Kamu tidak harus menceritakan tentang diri kamu atau pengalaman kamu sendiri, namun biasanya kamu memiliki ikatan emosional dan pengetahuan yang lebih tentang cerita yang ingin kamu angkat.</p>\n<p>Pertama coba buat beberapa <em>premis</em> (tema cerita), kemudian jika sudah memilih, buatlah <em>plot sinopsis</em> (cerita singkat) dari premis itu. <em>Oya</em>, kamu juga harus memutuskan apakah komik ini nantinya akan panjang (berseri) atau beberapa episode atau beberapa halaman langsung tamat (one-shot), dan jangan lupa tentunya untuk memilih judul komik yang menarik.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_393\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-393\" data-attachment-id=\"393\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/fourger2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fourger2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-393 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2.jpg\" alt=\"Contoh Premis dan Plot Fourger Inc\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-393\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Contoh Premis dan Plot Fourger Inc</p></div>\n<p>Komik kamu harus memiliki plot yang menarik, tidak peduli genre apa yang kamu pilih apakah itu horor, action, slice of life, ataupun romance. Kamu dapat menciptakan bagan struktur cerita untuk pegangan kamu sendiri untuk memastikan bahwa alur cerita kamu memiliki ritme yang baik dan agar para pembaca kamu dapat menangkap apa yang ingin kamu ceritakan dengan baik.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"394\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/fourger1-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fourger1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394 aligncenter\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger1-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>2. Buatlah karakter-karakter yang ada di ceritamu itu.<br />\nDi dalam sebuah cerita memiliki 2 jenis karakter yaitu karakter utama dan karakter figuran. Karakter-karakter ini memiliki sifat protagonis (baik), antagonis (jahat) dan ada yang berada di grey area (abu-abu, bisa jahat dan bisa baik).</p>\n<p>Kamu bisa mulai menuliskan konsep karakter yang ingin kamu ciptakan, dan membuat beberapa sketsa serta model sheet dari karakter tersebut.</p>\n<p><img data-attachment-id=\"395\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/fourger3-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fourger3\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-395 aligncenter\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger3-1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_314\" style=\"width: 330px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-314\" data-attachment-id=\"314\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/komik2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"320,450\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Komik2\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2-213x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-314 size-full\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2.jpg\" width=\"320\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2.jpg 320w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik2-213x300.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-314\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Contoh konsep karakter Justin Bruce</p></div>\n<p>3. Tentukan style dan buatlah beberapa draft kasar komik kamu tersebut</p>\n<p>Ada banyak style komik di dunia ini, namun jika kamu membidik pasar Asia tentunya style komik Manga ada di urutan teratas, disusul dengan style komik barat dan komik lokal yang dipengaruhi oleh gaya Amerika dan Eropa.</p>\n<p>Coba mulai membuat beberapa slice sketsa komik tanpa shading dan coloring dengan beberapa style. Jika kamu sudah puas, baru lanjut ke shading dan coloring, dan mulailah membuat episode pertama mu!</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_313\" style=\"width: 330px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-313\" data-attachment-id=\"313\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/komik1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"320,450\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Komik1\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1-213x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-313\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1.jpg 320w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik1-213x300.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-313\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sketsa kasar Fourger Inc</p></div>\n<p>4. Coba dapatkan feedback dari pembaca komik</p>\n<p>Jangan takut mendapatkan kritikan dan masukan dari konsumenmu langsung yaitu dari pembaca komik di kolom komentar. Coba upload karyamu ke ciayo.com/challenge atau bisa email ke submission@ciayo.com. CIAYO Comics menerima komik yang dibuat digital maupun dengan cara manual. Jika kamu menggambar manual, maka kamu harus melakukan scan terlebih dahulu sebelum bisa dikirim ke CIAYO Comics.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_396\" style=\"width: 330px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-396\" data-attachment-id=\"396\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/fourger4-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"320,450\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Fourger4\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1-213x300.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-396\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1.jpg\" alt=\"Tata cara submit CIAYO One-Shot Challenge (ciayo.com/challenge/submit)\" width=\"320\" height=\"450\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1.jpg 320w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Fourger4-1-213x300.jpg 213w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 320px) 100vw, 320px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-396\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Tata cara submit CIAYO One-Shot Challenge (ciayo.com/challenge/submit)</p></div>\n<p>5. Buat jadwal tayang tetap untuk komikmu</p>\n<p>Hal ini sepertinya sepele namun sangat penting. Jika kamu tidak bisa konsisten menayangkan komikmu, maka kamu akan kehilangan pembaca setia karena biasanya pembaca komik yang fanatik akan selalu menantikan jadwal tayang komik kesayangannya itu.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_318\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-318\" data-attachment-id=\"318\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/5-langkah-bikin-komik-ala-komikus-profesional/attachment/komik6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Komik6\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-318\" src=\"http://blog.ciayo.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/Komik6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-318\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Jadwal kerja Fourger Inc</p></div>\n<p>gimana tips nya? mantap kan! bisa kalian coba nih tipsnya dan jangan takut untung berkarya siapa tahu gambar meme komik, komik misteri, komik action, komik drama, komik komedi dan genre lainnya hasil karya kalian bisa disukain banyak orang! so keep trying guys !</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"4379d34d-bb24-5cc6-87e4-3ad9b27f01c7"}}}